50|$|Emergency Social Services now named Emergency Support Services {{provides}} short-term {{assistance to}} British Columbians who {{are forced to}} leave their homes because of <b>fire,</b> <b>floods,</b> earthquakes or other emergencies. This assistance includes food, lodging, clothing, emotional support and family reunification.|$|R
